<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"has-text-align-center world-intro","style":{"typography":{"textAlign":"center"},"color":{"text":"#ffffff"}},"fontSize":"2xl","fontFamily":"cormorant-garamond"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center world-intro has-text-color has-cormorant-garamond-font-family has-2-xl-font-size" style="color:#ffffff">Three hundred years ago, four founders built a city and placed a gem at its heart. The histories call them heroes. The gem knows better.</p>
